HUGA OPTOTECH IN said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 40.33% to NT$221,752,000 from NT$371,622,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            221,752          371,622    
YOY%             -40.33%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            846,083         1,546,915   
YOY%             -45.31% 
=================================================================
 